Name: The Nimbus Chorale: Order of Nature
AttributesDescription: A musical record found in Nimbus Sanctum. This chorale was performed by the people of Rinascita long before the Order's founding.
BgDescription: "We thank the cycle of day and night, the ever-shifting seasons, for they have kept hope alive in the darkness and have taught us to look forward to the harvest even in the coldest winters."
